    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You concentrate fire chakra in the soles of your feet and the palms of your hands, creating jets of exhaust that lift you up. While concentrating on this jutsu you have a flying speed of 40 feet and can hover. When you use your action to cast a jutsu with the Fire Release keyword, you can dash or disengage as a bonus action.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and increase your flying speed by 10 feet.</p>",
